m3_tire_factory Â© 2010

This map is made by me from the scratch and i hope you will like it!

Both teams spawns with an m3 shotgun, HE and of course a knife. Go on 3 different ways:
Left flank, Right flank or in to the factory building. Eliminate the oppenents with your m3
(or humiliate them with the knife) to win the round.

Maximum players: 64
